title: The Apothecary Diaries (Kusuriya no Hitorigoto)
description: A sharp-witted apothecary navigates palace intrigue using medicine, logic, and an unshakable sense of curiosity.

title: Kaminaki Sekai no Kamisama Katsudou (KamiKatsu)
description: A cultless god, an unwilling prophet, and escalating absurdity collide in a shameless parody of belief systems.

title: Undead Unluck
description: People cursed with negation powers clash with fate, death, and a universe that enforces cruel rules.

title: Frieren: Beyond Journey's End
description: An elf mage reflects on mortality, memory, and quiet grief long after the hero's journey ends.

title: The Hero Is Dead! (Yuusha ga Shinda!)
description: A shamelessly trashy fantasy comedy that commits hard to crude jokes, dumb luck, and anti-hero energy.
